Started off relatively amusing, calling out the narrative quirks and handwaving that goes into SCP writing.

It loses a lot of momentum in the various -4 entries, where it begins to lean less on the meta and seems to be content simply falling into the tropes its satirizing. It starts simply spewing out bs without retaining the tounge in cheek tone it sets out with.

And by the end this is absent entirely, with it resolving to lambast an edgy and OP superweapon.

The D-Class portion got a chuckle out of me, but overall it's too dull for me to want to upvote. -1







